com.aylanetworks.aylasdk

类 AylaUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaUser

  • public class AylaUser
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing information about the owner of the signed-in account. May be obtained via AylaSessionManager.fetchUserProfile(Response.Listener, ErrorListener) or modified via AylaSessionManager.updateUserProfile(AylaUser, Response.Listener, ErrorListener).
